### 50

### YOSHITAKA FUJIWARA

### FUJIWARA NO YOSHITAKA

<div style="margin-left: 32px">

  Kimi ga tame  
Oshikarazarishi  
  Inochi sae  
Nagaku mogana to  
Omoi keru kana.

DEATH had no terrors, Life no joys,  
  Before I met with thee;  
But now I fear, however long  
  My life may chance to be,  
  ’Twill be too short for me!

</div>

<span class="small">Yoshitaka died in the year 974. See verse No.
[18](hvj019.htm#page_18.md) for a note of the Fujiwara family.</span>

